{"tid":1699009,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[聽到想嘔系列] Mike Bloomberg: 習近平非常聆聽民意","createTime":"2019-11-08T01:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T15:02:28.000Z","uid":236171,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"372bc465d2ae80c19e2a2727f0547bef59ce8131","tid":1699009,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:44:09.000Z","msg":"睇下身為Bloomberg CEO、前紐約市長（連任三屆）嘅Mike Bloomberg 有咩想講<br />\n<br />\n呢個人有意成為民主黨總統候選人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下對話發生於一場美國電視清談節目。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">有咩辦法令中、印等國合作減低碳排放？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>Bloomberg: </strong></span>中國做咗好多嘢架（無視印度）。雖然佢哋用燃煤發電，但係佢哋將發電廠搬離城市，減少空氣污染（喂，冇解決過碳排放問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中共為咗繼續當權，佢哋非常原意聆聽民意</span></strong>（吓，我有冇聽錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">習近平唔係一個獨裁者</span></strong>。當人民話好難抖氣，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>習近平要回應選佢出嚟嘅人（人大）嘅意見</strong></span>，唔係佢難以繼續掌權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">吓你覺得習近平唔係獨裁者？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔使投票，無人選佢。唯一要驚嘅係咪得全國革命呢？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong> Bloomberg:</strong></span>中國唔會有革命架喇。冇一個國家政府喺得唔到全國大部分人支持下係可以持續掌權嘅，OK? 唔聽民意你估佢哋想變蘇聯咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">你覺得聆聽人民對新鮮空氣嘅意願就係民主？咁香港呢？佢哋遊行咗咁耐中共有冇聽過佢哋民意？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong> Bloomberg:</strong></span> 無視香港問題，繼續講北京點回應本土空氣污染問題（冇講過減少碳排放）。廢話一堆，唔翻譯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：Mike Bloomberg已經成為咗支共代言人，而家佢仲想選總統。大家自求多福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PA7v6n8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPA7v6n8.jpg&h=c3ec90d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認住佢個樣：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5neuCvb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5neuCvb.jpg&h=d5a00c7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f69434c38c645d709c150b124dd3585b564964d1","tid":1699009,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:44:51.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/FiringLineShow/status/1177397448320458753?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFiringLineShow%2Fstatus%2F1177397448320458753%3Fs%3D19&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUnPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=1698f442\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFiringLineShow%2Fstatus%2F1177397448320458753%3Fs%3D19&h=51e6b1fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FiringLineShow/status/1177397448320458753?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"eff88bd90a2a389d54a99ce6c008b226b5aa04a3","tid":1699009,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:49:18.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"fba133e5f3ca521af1b836fb59b196f041ee00a4","tid":1699009,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:53:28.000Z","msg":"會唔會係曲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n六四無死人、袁木好誠實、中國有民主、習主席唔係甴近平小熊維尼"},{"pid":"2b93e71257d682afd94ec33249f1f29b5f106346","tid":1699009,"uid":101756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:56:51.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"bf8e418b5191c4a7516f1b94c2a45fbd588a6589","tid":1699009,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba133e5f3ca521af1b836fb59b196f041ee00a4